  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_validation-levels.dita" xtrc="shortdesc:1;23:14">Every rule in a rule set has a level: <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_validation-levels.dita" xtrc="b:1;23:55">Required</b> or <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_validation-levels.dita" xtrc="b:2;23:74">Suggested</b>.
  Required failures block your CI pipeline. Suggested failures appear in the report
  as recommendations and do not block a merge.</shortdesc>

